DIE dag van die Champ­ions! Dít is hoe Sondag se Coca-Cola Cup-program op William Herbert in Wynberg beskou kan word wanneer die Round of 64 van die mans beslis word. Ses van die vorige kampioenspanne in dié kompetisie sal op dié veld in aksie wees. En in twee van dié wedstryde kom van hulle teen mekaar te staan. Daar sal met groot belangstelling gekyk word wat gebeur in die stryd tussen Silver Spurs, kampioen in 2014, en Liverpool-Portland. Die span van Portland het jare gelede sokker in die Kaap heeltemal oorheers en is nou besig om weer groot hoogtes te bereik. Liverpool-Portland het in 1996 en 2000 dié gesogte uitkloptitel gewen. Jordan Callies (2013) van Rygate en Young Pirates (2016) van Heideveld is ook vorige champions wat mekaar die stryd aansê. Coach Roger Fortune se Pirates (2016) sal wil wys dat hulle oorwinning van 16-0 in die vorige ronde teen Thornhill United geen gelukskoot was nie. Young Idols van Manenberg het in 2015 in dié kompetisie sukses behaal en sal hul aanslag wil lewend hou wanneer die studente van CPUT aangedurf word. En asof dit nie genoeg champions material op skou is nie, kom Hanover Park, wat in 2009 en 2012 met die titel weggestap het, teen MA Colville van Mitchells Plain te staan. Premier United, een van die suksesvolste spanne in dié kompetisie, sal op The Greens in Manenberg ook nog in die prentjie wil bly wanneer hy Beacon Spurs van Mitchells Plain pak. Rygersdal, 2017 se kampioen, kom ook op Johnson Road teen Game Yethu te staan. SONDAG MANS William Herbert, Wynberg 13:30: A: Seaside Spurs (Two Oceans) t Delft (Delft); B: Jordan Callies (Rygate) t Young Pirates (Heideveld); C: Silver Spurs (CT Tygerberg) t Liverpool-Portland (M. Plain); D: Ma Colville (Mitchells Plain) t Hanover Park (CT Tygerberg). 15:30: A: Junior Pirates (Simunye) t Saxon Rovers (CT Tygerberg); B: Young Idols (Manenberg) t CPUT (Northerns); C: Tableview (CT Tygerberg) t Rebels (Lingelethu); D: Bellville-South (Northerns) t Ruitewacht (CT Tygerberg). Johnson Road, Rylands 13:30: A: United FC (Northerns) t Atlantis Leeds (Atlantis); B: D&G Orient (Rygate) t Crystal Palace (Manenberg); C: Rising Stars (Goodhope) t Wesley United (Cape District); D: Wynberg St. Johns (CT Tygerberg) t MPCE (M. Plain); E: Two For Joy (Helderberg) t Primrose Park (Manenberg); F: FC Manenberg (Manenberg) t JL Zwane (Gugulethu). 15:30: A: Saltriver Celtics (Rygate) t Flamingo (Langa); B: Green Lovers (Oostenberg) t Clover (Mandalay); C: Electric City United (Greater Bluedowns) t Elsies River United (Northerns); D: Celtic FC (Simunye) t Vasco da Gama (CT Tygerberg); E: Oasis FC (South Peninsula) t Valencia FC (Makhaza); F: Game Yethu (Greater Philippi) t Rygersdal (CT Tygerberg). The Greens, Manenberg 13:30: A: Ulana Academy (Mandalay) t Mthatha/Orient/YBC FC (Nyanga); B: Diadora (Athone) t Edgemead (CT Tygerberg); C: Piranha (Greater Philippi) t Royal Citizens (Mandalay). 15:30: A: UCT (CT Tygerberg) t FC Cafda (Cape District); B: Beacon Spurs (Mitchells Plain) t Premier United (Hanover Park); C: South End (Rylands) t CT Falcons (Greater Philippi). Lingelethu, Khayelitsha 13:30: A: Super Eagles (Mandalay) t Juventus (Greater Philippi); B: City Kings t Flamingo (Greater Philippi); C: Westridge (Mitchells Plain) t Clarewood (Cape District). 15:30: A: 7 Attackers (Greater Philippi) t FC Tafelzucht (Mitchells Plain); B: Bishop Lavis (Northerns) t Belhar Stars (Northerns); Juventus (M. Plain) t Juventus (Lingelethu). O.18-SEUNS William Herbert 10:45: A: New Ages (Bloekombos) t Bluedowns Spurs (Northerns); B: Bayhill United (Mitchells Plain) t Belinda FC (Nyanga); C: FC Porto (Greater Philippi) t Rygersdal (CT Tygerberg); D: Belhar Spurs (Northerns) t D&G Orient (Rygate). 12:00: A: Try Again (Oostenberg) t Ocean View (Cape District); Grassy Park United (Cape District) t Everton United (Heideveld); Juventus (M. Plain) t Tramway (CT Tygerberg); Helderberg Rovers (Helderberg) t CT Spurs (CT Tygerberg). Johnson Road, Rygate 10:45: A: Connoisseur Spurs (Rygate) t Pro Stars (MPFD); B: Liverpool (Du Noon) t Durbanville (CT Tygerberg); C: CT City (Nyanga) t Onesimo Football Academy (MPFD); D: Hellenic (CT Tygerberg) t Table View (CT Tygerberg); E: Ikapa Sporting (M. Plain) t Nova Nacional (Rygate); F: Cape Royal (Helderberg) t Ulana Academy (Mandalay). 12:00: A: Santos (Cape District) t Bayview (M. Plain); B: CT Pirates (Gugulethu) t Hanover Park (CT Tygerberg); C: Bellville United (Northerns) t SSS Academy (Athlone); D. Chaka Pioneers t CT Swallows (Greater Mfuleni); E: Riverside Rangers (Northerns) t Greenwood (Cape District); F: Mfolozi (Greater Philippi) t CS Abahlobo (Oostenberg). The Greens, Manenberg 10:45: A: Clover (Mandalay) t Junction Rovers (Rygate); B: Ubuntu (Two Oceans) t Electric City (Greater Blue Downs); C: Bafana United (Mandela Park) t Milano United (M. Plain). 12:00: A: Wolves (Cape District) t HBUFC (Goodhope); B: Harvest Academy (South Peninsula) t City Kings (Hanover Park); C: FC Tafelzucht (M. Plain) t Du Noon Sporting (Du Noon). Lingelethu, Khayelitsha 10:45: A: Woodlands United (Mitchells Plain) t Ravensmead (Northerns); B: Young Bafana (Helderberg) t Masithandane (Nyanga); C: Eerste River (Northerns) t Valhalla United (Northerns); 12:00: A: Jomo Power (Atlantis) t Inkanyanmba (Nyanga); B: Lion City (Langa) t FN Rangers (CT Tygerberg); C: Ashford Athletic (Cape District) t Stephanian Ottery (Cape District). VROUE Rooikrans-sportterrein, Grassy Park 11:00: A: Real Brazilians (Du Noon) t Burnley (Metropolitan); B: Rygate Ladies (Rygate) t East End (Hanover Park); C: Valhalla United (Northerns) t UCT (CT Tygerberg); D: Spurs (Cape District) t Liverpool-Portland (M. Plain)**; E: Ikamva Ladies (Nyanga) t Green Point Salesians (CT Tygerberg); F: RV United (Lingelethu) t Santos (Cape District). 12:30: A: Hanover Park (CT Tygerberg) t Macassar (Northerns). 13:00: B: Avendale Ladies (CT Tygerberg) t Invincible Cravenby (Northerns); C: Green Lovers (Greater Philippi) t Shosholoza (Hanover Park); D: Laven